            <title>[XGC-132] Add auto fallback when Java cannot read image</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/XGC-132</link>
                <project id="12314221" key="XGC">XMLGraphicsCommons</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Workaround is to switch to Java 17 or use:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;image-loading&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;penalty value=&quot;-1000&quot; class=&quot;org.apache.xmlgraphics.image.loader.impl.PreloaderRawPNG&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/image-loading&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Under Java 11:&lt;br/&gt;
Caused by: java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException: readRaster not supported!&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.desktop/javax.imageio.ImageReader.readRaster(ImageReader.java:1284)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
